<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 20:07:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>一些人质家属的反内塔尼亚胡声明揭示了内部纠纷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-declaration-by-some-hostages-families-reveals-internal-disputes/0000018e-95ae-dd2f-a7cf-d7bf6a540000</link><description>经过数周的克制后，一些家庭呼吁驱逐内塔尼亚胡，因为与哈马斯的谈判明显陷入僵局。与此同时，其他家庭则认为此举过于对抗，并明确表示不同意</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 19:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-declaration-by-some-hostages-families-reveals-internal-disputes/0000018e-95ae-dd2f-a7cf-d7bf6a540000</guid></item><item><title>数万人在耶路撒冷集会，要求内塔尼亚胡下台；抗议者封锁道路、纵火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/hostages-dont-get-to-take-recess-but-somehow-they-can/0000018e-9582-dd2f-a7cf-d7bb8dbc0000</link><description>耶路撒冷的大规模集会和组织者计划在以色列议会外搭建的帐篷城是自 10 月 7 日以来的首次此类行动。“我不相信我必须与政府官员斗争才能获得我兄弟返回家园的权利，”人质的姐姐说</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 19:12:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/hostages-dont-get-to-take-recess-but-somehow-they-can/0000018e-9582-dd2f-a7cf-d7bb8dbc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长阻止内塔尼亚胡绕过最高法院停止犹太基金的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/ag-blocks-netanyahus-efforts-to-bypass-top-court-ruling-stopping-yeshiva-funds/0000018e-94fc-da88-afff-f5fd540b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理组建了一个特别小组，负责寻找方法规避高等法院冻结其学生拒绝参军的犹太学院预算的命令。总检察长迄今为止阻止了这一举措，称所有选择都将违反该命令</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 17:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/ag-blocks-netanyahus-efforts-to-bypass-top-court-ruling-stopping-yeshiva-funds/0000018e-94fc-da88-afff-f5fd540b0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们不需要非犹太人的恩惠”：内塔尼亚胡政府是一个辛辣的讽刺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-31/ty-article/.highlight/we-dont-need-favors-from-the-goyim-netanyahus-government-is-a-bitter-irony/0000018e-9566-dd2f-a7cf-d77f48f90000</link><description>有些承诺以前被认为是国家与其公民之间契约的基础——床上安全；以明确的战略和道德界限来应对可怕的袭击。但这对于本届政府来说是完全陌生的</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 17:36:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-31/ty-article/.highlight/we-dont-need-favors-from-the-goyim-netanyahus-government-is-a-bitter-irony/0000018e-9566-dd2f-a7cf-d77f48f90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 177 天：以色列代表团抵达开罗进行人质释放会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-177-israeli-delegation-lands-in-cairo-for-hostage-release-talks/0000018e-9570-da88-afff-f57db4860000</link><description>以色列代表团抵达开罗参加人质释放谈判 ■ 据报道，以色列在黎巴嫩南部杀害了真主党高级官员 ■ 高级保守党议员声称英国收到了以色列在加沙违反国际法的法律建议 ■ 周四在约旦河西岸向以色列车辆开火的巴勒斯坦人■ 贝都因以色列男子在贝尔谢巴刺伤士兵后被枪杀 ■ 战争结束 177 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 17:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-177-israeli-delegation-lands-in-cairo-for-hostage-release-talks/0000018e-9570-da88-afff-f57db4860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院推翻了对阻挡警察水炮的著名反内塔尼亚胡活动人士的定罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/court-overturns-conviction-of-anti-netanyahu-activist-who-blocked-police-water-cannon/0000018e-94df-da88-afff-f5ffe32b0000</link><description>反对内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议运动领导人戈南·本·伊扎克承认，他故意干扰水炮的使用，因为警察即将以危及示威者的方式使用水炮。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 14:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/court-overturns-conviction-of-anti-netanyahu-activist-who-blocked-police-water-cannon/0000018e-94df-da88-afff-f5ffe32b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙设立了“杀戮区”。任何闯入其中的人都会被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-created-kill-zones-in-gaza-anyone-who-crosses-into-them-is-shot/0000018e-946c-d4de-afee-f46da9ee0000</link><description>以色列军队称，自加沙战争爆发以来，已有 9000 名恐怖分子被打死。然而，国防官员和士兵告诉国土报，这些人往往是平民，他们唯一的罪行就是越过以色列国防军划定的无形界限</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 13:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-created-kill-zones-in-gaza-anyone-who-crosses-into-them-is-shot/0000018e-946c-d4de-afee-f46da9ee0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷最后的绿地之一的争夺战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-battle-over-one-of-the-last-undeveloped-hills-in-jerusalem/0000018e-9423-d4de-afee-f42f67a00000</link><description>吉瓦特哈塔纳赫 (Givat Hatanach) 计划建设一座新的酒店综合体，这是该市仅存的几座未开发的山丘之一。居民和专家警告当地自然环境和历史城堡受到破坏，而英国政府则严重关注其对现场苏格兰教堂的影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 11:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-battle-over-one-of-the-last-undeveloped-hills-in-jerusalem/0000018e-9423-d4de-afee-f42f67a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列央行行长表示，加沙战争期间未来的国防支出需要更加明确</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/israels-central-bank-chief-says-more-clarity-on-defense-spending-needed-amid-gaza-war/0000018e-943a-d229-adae-95fb05260000</link><description>以色列立法者批准在 2024 年国家预算中增加数十亿谢克尔，以资助以色列对抗哈马斯的战争，因为战争目标的不确定性和加沙计划的“后天”迫在眉睫</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 11:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/israels-central-bank-chief-says-more-clarity-on-defense-spending-needed-amid-gaza-war/0000018e-943a-d229-adae-95fb05260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军军官在以色列南部发生持刀袭击事件中受轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-officer-stabbed-in-suspected-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-9372-d4de-afee-f37f57970000</link><description>这名 28 岁的袭击者是贝都因市拉哈特的居民，在刺伤后被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 08:38:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-officer-stabbed-in-suspected-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-9372-d4de-afee-f37f57970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极端正统派领导人表示内塔尼亚胡的联盟不会因正统军队征兵而崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/as-draft-exemption-expires-ultra-orthodox-leaders-signal-coalition-wont-collapse/0000018e-90dc-d229-adae-91df8bea0000</link><description>尽管以色列极端正统派社区感到愤怒，但联盟领导人并不认为犹太学院学生服兵役的政治危机会对依赖正统政党的总理内塔尼亚胡的联盟构成直接威胁</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 02:43:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/as-draft-exemption-expires-ultra-orthodox-leaders-signal-coalition-wont-collapse/0000018e-90dc-d229-adae-91df8bea0000</guid></item><item><title>为期四天的集会在耶路撒冷拉开帷幕，反内塔尼亚胡抗议运动面临考验</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-govt-protest-to-peak-in-jerusalem-ahead-of-knesset-recess/0000018e-90f5-d9a4-a7bf-dcfdccd30000</link><description>以色列针对内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议运动计划在耶路撒冷议会外建立一个帐篷城，以疏导公众的愤怒，以确保议会春季休会前有强劲的投票率</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 02:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-govt-protest-to-peak-in-jerusalem-ahead-of-knesset-recess/0000018e-90f5-d9a4-a7bf-dcfdccd30000</guid></item><item><title>周五，以色列士兵在加沙地带的火箭弹袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-live/police-clash-with-anti-govt-protesters-16-arrested-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-9214-d8cd-a9ce-977660560000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡将在全身麻醉下接受疝气手术 ■ 以色列国防军袭击加沙医院附近的伊斯兰圣战中心 ■ 贝尔谢巴刺伤事件造成一人受伤 ■ 以色列代表团抵达开罗就停火、释放人质协议进行谈判</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 01:30:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-live/police-clash-with-anti-govt-protesters-16-arrested-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-9214-d8cd-a9ce-977660560000</guid></item><item><title>由于缺乏经济复苏和以色列援助，巴勒斯坦新政府将难以运作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/lacking-economic-recovery-and-israeli-aid-new-palestinian-govt-will-struggle-to-function/0000018e-90a0-d229-adae-91f35b5b0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦新总理穆罕默德·穆斯塔法称约旦河西岸的经济形势是灾难性的，居民们知道，如果没有国际社会的经济安全网，政府的成功最多也将是有限的</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 20:12:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/lacking-economic-recovery-and-israeli-aid-new-palestinian-govt-will-struggle-to-function/0000018e-90a0-d229-adae-91f35b5b0000</guid></item><item><title>在土地日游行中，数千名巴勒斯坦人和阿拉伯以色列人抗议加沙战争的“种族灭绝”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/in-land-day-march-thousands-of-palestinians-arab-israelis-protest-gaza-war/0000018e-90c4-d229-adae-91d787070000</link><description>以色列警方允许游行进行，但条件是不得悬挂巴勒斯坦国旗，声称这可能“导致公共秩序混乱”。组织者决定遵守命令，用巴勒斯坦国旗的颜色写反战口号</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 19:55:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/in-land-day-march-thousands-of-palestinians-arab-israelis-protest-gaza-war/0000018e-90c4-d229-adae-91d787070000</guid></item><item><title>数千人在特拉维夫集会，被释放的人质指责内塔尼亚胡政府在加沙抛弃以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostage-accuses-govt-of-abandoning-israelis-in-gaza-as-thousands-rally-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-9041-def1-a58f-f47909760000</link><description>纪念哈马斯被囚禁的第 176 天，家人将自己关在舞台上的笼子里，呼吁立即达成协议。一名获释人质向内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们讲话时说，“不要再处理不重要的法律了”，并补充说：“你们的行为就像谈判是小孩子的游戏一样”</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 18:03:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostage-accuses-govt-of-abandoning-israelis-in-gaza-as-thousands-rally-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-9041-def1-a58f-f47909760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 176 天：以色列国防军称哈马斯高级成员在 Al-Shifa 医院行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-176-idf-says-senior-hamas-members-killed-in-al-shifa-operation/0000018e-9055-d9a4-a7bf-dc5d1d7c0000</link><description>以色列国防军：三名哈马斯高级成员在 Al-Shifa 袭击中丧生 ■ 以色列推动建立多国部队以确保援助交付 ■ 四名联合国工作人员在黎巴嫩南部受伤；以色列国防军否认参与其中 ■ 以色列国防军在 13 岁巴勒斯坦人被军队枪杀后展开调查 ■ 据称以色列周五对叙利亚发动袭击，导致 52 人死亡 ■ 战争结束 176 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 17:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-176-idf-says-senior-hamas-members-killed-in-al-shifa-operation/0000018e-9055-d9a4-a7bf-dc5d1d7c0000</guid></item><item><title>数千名以色列人加入人质家庭参加大规模集会，警察与反内塔尼亚胡抗议者发生冲突； 16人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/protests-against-netanyahus-govt-in-support-for-hostage-release-break-out-across-israel/0000018e-9000-d229-adae-91d3fb440000</link><description>抗议者封锁了特拉维夫主要高速公路，加沙被扣押人质家属宣布争取人质释放协议的斗争升级，警察和抗议者之间爆发冲突。以色列各地数千人示威反对政府，呼吁提前选举</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 16:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/protests-against-netanyahus-govt-in-support-for-hostage-release-break-out-across-israel/0000018e-9000-d229-adae-91d3fb440000</guid></item><item><title>四名联合国工作人员在黎巴嫩联黎部队车辆袭击中受伤；以色列否认参与</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/four-un-staff-wounded-in-unifil-vehicle-strike-in-lebanon-israel-denies-involvement/0000018e-8fb3-def1-a58f-efbb64590000</link><description>联黎部队表示，受伤人员已被疏散接受治疗，目前仍在调查爆炸起因。以色列立即否认参与该事件</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 14:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/four-un-staff-wounded-in-unifil-vehicle-strike-in-lebanon-israel-denies-involvement/0000018e-8fb3-def1-a58f-efbb64590000</guid></item><item><title>13岁巴勒斯坦少年在约旦河西岸被枪杀 以色列军队“澄清”事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/13-year-old-palestinian-shot-dead-in-west-bank-israeli-army-clarifying-incident/0000018e-8f9d-d9a4-a7bf-cfdd08110000</link><description>约旦河西岸城镇卡巴蒂亚的消息人士称，以色列军队连夜进行了一次突袭，造成另外两名巴勒斯坦青年受伤，其中一人重伤；另一名巴勒斯坦青年受伤。以色列国防军表示，他们向向他们开枪的恐怖分子进行了还击</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 14:12:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/13-year-old-palestinian-shot-dead-in-west-bank-israeli-army-clarifying-incident/0000018e-8f9d-d9a4-a7bf-cfdd08110000</guid></item></channel></rss>